{"id": "ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 145, "displayName": {"text": "Phu's Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbFIyMVJUalZXYlRkMVJtVm9Oa1JJVVRKaFkyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Portuguese egg tarts are really tasty, the filling is just sweet enough and the size of each tart is perfect. Not the flakiest crust, if that’s what you like, but definitely worth grabbing a box!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Portuguese egg tarts are really tasty, the filling is just sweet enough and the size of each tart is perfect. Not the flakiest crust, if that’s what you like, but definitely worth grabbing a box!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brian Lupo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117029832485022780852/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIF_Qals7vZFxqsjnowGwOyFF_oC-XRiHW2cKT5NpkbkjHtQw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-26T01:20:34.014254210Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbFIyMVJUalZXYlRkMVJtVm9Oa1JJVVRKaFkyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbFIyMVJUalZXYlRkMVJtVm9Oa1JJVVRKaFkyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d07b9f3654b9:0x102674b2cf4af67"}, {"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLU0Y0NHZmNGJMRG1RRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "We always come here for the Portuguese Egg Tarts only ($2 each) and parking is always terrible on the weekends. It is located in a very busy plaza on Garvey. The tarts are always good and fresh, creamy and crunchy. This chef who used to work at Jim’s Bakery. The store front and inside aint pretty so dont bring your date here. Custom service is a hit or miss. Minimum for credit card is $20. Sometimes they do sold out so call before going!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We always come here for the Portuguese Egg Tarts only ($2 each) and parking is always terrible on the weekends. It is located in a very busy plaza on Garvey. The tarts are always good and fresh, creamy and crunchy. This chef who used to work at Jim’s Bakery. The store front and inside aint pretty so dont bring your date here. Custom service is a hit or miss. Minimum for credit card is $20. Sometimes they do sold out so call before going!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Davy Situ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117529409514676004575/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUq-LtvqmG_BYBFr0a4jFQPgNp0-y1M3IDYPmWqz4AX3PZj1cws=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-15T23:32:50.026358Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLU0Y0NHZmNGJMRG1RRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLU0Y0NHZmNGJMRG1RRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d07b9f3654b9:0x102674b2cf4af67"}, {"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLdHRucGZ3EAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The Portuguese egg tarts are great here but they also sell other baked goods and cakes. The location is located in a nondescript strip mall with plenty of parking.  On the weekends, there could sometimes be a small line of customers.  They require a minimum of $20 for credit card charges.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The Portuguese egg tarts are great here but they also sell other baked goods and cakes. The location is located in a nondescript strip mall with plenty of parking.  On the weekends, there could sometimes be a small line of customers.  They require a minimum of $20 for credit card charges.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Simon Lau", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103697346167585249774/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQbdT0VOKktVe2Cg4MogWoqIjYF98rzVevTgJF_nrQH7HqDNE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2021-05-11T03:41:14.062828Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLdHRucGZ3EAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLdHRucGZ3EAE!2m1!1s0x80c2d07b9f3654b9:0x102674b2cf4af67"}, {"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURoemNQS0hREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The egg tarts are delicious!  I’ve ate the famous egg tarts in Portugal but they were dense and too sweet compared to these.  Closed to go inside the store, only order at the door with one person working.  Be prepared for a long line on the weekends.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The egg tarts are delicious!  I’ve ate the famous egg tarts in Portugal but they were dense and too sweet compared to these.  Closed to go inside the store, only order at the door with one person working.  Be prepared for a long line on the weekends.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Duy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103813134984278623105/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkQazx71qGjeumXVzsckvtDbm1UQu03WE9R6j6ERQLjy8u9hY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2023-03-14T21:31:39.338970Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURoemNQS0hREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURoemNQS0hREAE!2m1!1s0x80c2d07b9f3654b9:0x102674b2cf4af67"}, {"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXMTc3UGh3RRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 years ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "After trying it at my friend's place, I got to get me some of these. One of the best egg tarts I have ever had. The egg custard is very delicious, excellent creaminess, and it doesn't taste too eggy. The crust has a great crunchiness to it, very flaky. 1 dozen for $18, I believe it is a good price, each of the tarts is pretty big. My wife and I love it very much.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "After trying it at my friend's place, I got to get me some of these. One of the best egg tarts I have ever had. The egg custard is very delicious, excellent creaminess, and it doesn't taste too eggy. The crust has a great crunchiness to it, very flaky. 1 dozen for $18, I believe it is a good price, each of the tarts is pretty big. My wife and I love it very much.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Julius Marzuki", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103921448574192344333/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9hx8UJ_LeidfrEscLjmlmIu42K7vmCYfuogCn2WwX4IFSrTSwlQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2022-03-09T05:29:33.087213Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXMTc3UGh3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXMTc3UGh3RRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d07b9f3654b9:0x102674b2cf4af67"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJuVQ2n3vQwoARZ6_0LEtnAgE/photos/AWCwydgdWnTU29M4Imj23zBfIEXaC2gCR6cvelyStULSTgvZm_IA-C1_iM_OGfWTRBD8jiVp6k5tvRLEromuCOj3tpl12EDfIOzlfbbmmG6h_Q0YI0pZLXh8xk--jLMwxhX6TewC6n7RWCIJHFAUUVXDzLvuJZWnKpwClADwlOb7Ln-ZbrKmH8zMVo5MwvZNK61pBtEA6Gy9clhpnGYSzYFO69HXmYeuN_u0nf82y5GxsIb15npKHS6Y-0ZBrfFtjI5owcjQCQl-syKZe74QtIXkzCuFYE7Rxrtkjm3PnhOjhSlAbd8skArBJXeWT92Dkx8tFLiEwo66PbfvUG6eXckGum1sb5AgKR